This AWS CodeBuild buildspec (v0.2) automates Dockerized application deployment. In the pre-build phase, it captures the commit ID and logs into Amazon ECR. The build phase uses Docker Compose to build and tag the image. In the post-build phase, it logs completion time and pushes the Docker image to Amazon ECR. This concise pipeline streamlines the build and deployment process for containerized applications.
